<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>Display Student Page</title>
<meta charset="utf-8" />
</head>
<body>

<p>Setup the service details. In Kubernetes, each service
is given a unique IP address known as the Cluster IP and
a service port number (aka &quot;port&quot;) that was specified during the service declaration.
</p>
<form action="" method="post">
<br/><label for="service-type">Service Type:</label>
<select id="service-type" name="service-type">
  <option value="clusterip">Cluster IP: Internal to Cluster: Container to Container</option>
  <option value="nodeport">Node Port: Internal or external talk to pods via node</option>
  <option value="lb">Load Balancer: External direct to a service which select node/pods</option>
  <option value="ingress">Ingress: External to different services by URL (port 80 or 443)</option>
  <option value="internal">Internal to Pod: Container to Container (not a service)</option>
</select>
<div id="service-details"></div>
<select id="service-action" name="service-action">
  <option value="get">GET</option>
  <option value="post">POST</option>
  <option value="put">PUT</option>
  <option value="patch">PATCH</option>
  <option value="delete">DELETE</option>
</select>
<br/><label for="path-textbox">Path (if reqd):</label>
<span id="path-prefix"></span><input id="path-textbox" name="path-textbox" type="text" value="" />

<br/><label for="req-body-textbox">JSON Body:</label><input id="req-body-textbox" name="req-body-textbox" type="text" disabled />
<br/><input id="action-button" type="button" value="Send Request"/>
</form>
<div id="status" border=1>Status Waiting...</div>
<br/>

<form action="" method="post">
<br/><label for="getp-ip-textbox">Cluster IP (or container name within pod):</label>
<input id="getp-ip-textbox" name="getp-ip-textbox" type="text" value="k8s-pod" />
<br/><label for="getp-port-textbox">Service Port:</label>
<input id="getp-port-textbox" name="getp-port-textbox" type="text" value="1339" />
<input id="start-poll-button" type="button" value="Start Poll"/>
<input id="stop-poll-button" type="button" value="Stop Poll" disabled />
</form>
<div id="pods">Pods&colon;<br/></div>

<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.min.js" integrity="sha256-9/aliU8dGd2tb6OSsuzixeV4y/faTqgFtohetphbbj0=" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
<script src="./index.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
